---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Agentic AI Notebooks - Drizby"
  description="Multi-turn AI conversations about your data. Ask questions in natural language and get visualizations, insights, and actionable results."
  ogImage="https://www.drizby.com/images/drizby_3.png"
  canonicalPath="/features/agentic-notebooks"
>
  <main class="feature-page">
    <a href="/" class="breadcrumb">&larr; Back to Home</a>

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Agentic AI Notebooks</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">Have a conversation with your data</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="screenshot-container">
        <figure>
          <img src="/images/drizby_3.png" alt="Drizby agentic AI notebook with charts and markdown" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption>Multi-turn AI conversations with visualizations and insights</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="card card-highlight">
        <h2>Multi-turn AI Conversations</h2>
        <p>Ask questions about your data in natural language. The AI agent queries your semantic layer, generates visualizations, and provides insights. Follow up with more questions to dig deeper -- the agent remembers context across turns.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Mixed Content Blocks</h3>
          <p>Markdown, charts, query results, and KPI cards in one document. Each block type is rendered natively, creating rich analytical reports from a single conversation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Auto-save</h3>
          <p>Notebook state persists automatically with save status indicators. Never lose your work -- every change is saved in real-time as you explore your data.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Dashboard Promotion</h3>
          <p>Promote any notebook block into a full dashboard with a single click. Found an insight worth sharing? Turn it into a persistent dashboard portlet instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Configurable AI Provider</h3>
          <p>Works with Anthropic Claude, OpenAI, or Google Gemini. Choose the model that works best for your data and switch between providers from the settings page.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Per-notebook Connections</h3>
          <p>Each notebook can query a different database connection. Explore your production database in one notebook and your analytics warehouse in another.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Semantic Layer Queries</h3>
          <p>The AI agent queries through the semantic layer, not raw SQL. This means your cubes, measures, and dimensions are used for every query, ensuring consistency and security.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section cta-section">
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://github.com/cliftonc/drizby" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg class="gh-icon" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.013 8.013 0 0016 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"/></svg>
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a class="btn" href="https://cloud.drizby.com/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Try Drizby Cloud</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .feature-page {
    max-width: 1150px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .breadcrumb:hover { color: var(--accent-hover); }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text) 0%, var(--accent-hover) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .hero-desc {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .card h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .card p { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .card-highlight {
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--surface) 0%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05) 100%);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .screenshot-container figure {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .screenshot-container figure:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
  }
  .screenshot-container img { width: 100%; display: block; }
  .screenshot-container figcaption {
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-section { text-align: center; }
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  .btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--text); }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
    border-color: var(--accent-hover);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .gh-icon { width: 1em; height: 1em; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
